: basics
:
$* -g 1 <<EOI >>EOO
Hello, World!
EOI
00000000: 48 65 6c 6c 6f 2c 20 57 6f 72 6c 64 21 0a        Hello, World!.
EOO

: size
:
cat <<EOI >=input;
Hello, World!
EOI
$* -s -1 -l 1 input | sed -n -e 's/^([0-9a-f]+):.*$/\1/p' - >'0000000d'

: include
:
$* -i <<EOI >>EOO
Hello, World!
EOI
  0x48, 0x65, 0x6c, 0x6c, 0x6f, 0x2c, 0x20, 0x57, 0x6f, 0x72, 0x6c, 0x64,
  0x21, 0x0a
EOO
